metadata.name: Mata
metadata.description:
Mata Hari,  became one of the most iconic femmes fatale in history. The exotic dancer turned into a deadly double agent who used her abilities of seduction to obtain military secrets. Legend says that she blew a kiss to her firing squad as her final act in this world

“She lived her life in garish hues  
A seduction and delight  
The lady didn't sing the blues  
But conspired to steal the night” by crowfly
